    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Oath of Redemption sets a paladin on a difficult path, one that requires a holy warrior to use violence only as a last resort. Paladins who dedicate themselves to this oath believe that any person can be redeemed and that the path of benevolence and justice is one that anyone can walk. These paladins face evil creatures in the hope of turning them to the light, and the paladins slay them only when such a deed will clearly save other lives. Paladins who follow this path are known as redeemers.</p><p>While redeemers are idealists, they are no fools. Redeemers know that undead, demons, devils, and other supernatural threats can be inherently evil. Against such foes, the paladins bring the full wrath of their weapons and spells to bear. Yet the redeemers still pray that, one day, even creatures of wickedness will invite their own redemption.</p><h3>Oath of Redemption Spells</h3><table><thead><tr><td>Paladin Level</td><td>Spells</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3rd</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.6D4SqywIRCeJBtHa]{Sanctuary}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.ieouWH8zqoaYHPeG]{Sleep}</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.FITDsvKW3cQZt4t3]{Calm Emotions}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.NXOXaNWD6HazQkmY]{Hold Person}</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.fRhxAiPjKGsYpuNO]{Counterspell}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.9RJD2bLhnuVeh04i]{Hypnotic Pattern}</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.M6Gj97sn60ps3UMA]{Otiluke's Resilient Sphere}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.BmWgCc1hVRkNlQHf]{Stoneskin}</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.R6HwuSHAkPV4kAzF]{Hold Monster}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.5yIK1pP6TarIWxBo]{Wall of Force}</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Oath of the Crown Features</h3><p>3rd: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.05cYWPUjsW1as3DL]{Tenets of Redemption}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.dXkcXwaNJJoaA1uc]{Emissary of Peace}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.lL77jlcSjqNErEY8]{Rebuke the Violent}</p><p>7th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.ybOFs0lFFHgtsstD]{Aura of the Guardian}</p><p>15th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.2ec8pwYmgaKzTq00]{Protective Spirit}</p><p>20th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.RCSnyMxzq8qUTA0i]{Emissary of Redemption}</p>",
